RSTM Release 8 Notes

The latest RSTM release features the following changes:

- Native Support for the Intel Transactional C++ Compiler

Important Build Notes

- The svn branch must be configured before being built. Run the 'autogen'
  script from the root. This will generate the configure script.

Please visit the RSTM Google code site for more information:

http://code.google.com/p/rstm
